{"tid":618942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★超級巴士迷為把原裝巴士牌　安裝自己巴士上　認爆竊判入獄2年","createTime":"2018-04-06T08:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T08:20:43.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"29abdba2410f62a062717801668349698bbb8704","tid":618942,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T08:09:06.000Z","msg":"曾任職九巴的超級巴士迷，去年20歲生日當天凌晨，夥同兩位同道中人帶備工具，於屯門區連環爆竊3個巴士站站長室，偷走30塊巴士路線膠牌、27張巴士路線資料紙和3張巴士路牌貼紙。巴士迷日前承認3項串謀爆竊罪，法官判刑時斥被告行為十分幼稚及愚蠢，雖然犯案可能只是強求想將原裝巴士牌安裝在自己的巴士上，惟被告有組織地犯案並有同黨，今（6日）被判囚24個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/175465/%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E8%BF%B7%E7%82%BA%E6%8A%8A%E5%8E%9F%E8%A3%9D%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E7%89%8C-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E4%B8%8A-%E8%AA%8D%E7%88%86%E7%AB%8A%E5%88%A4%E5%85%A5%E7%8D%842%E5%B9%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F175465%2F%25E8%25B6%2585%25E7%25B4%259A%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%258A%258A%25E5%258E%259F%25E8%25A3%259D%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E7%2589%258C-%25E5%25AE%2589%25E8%25A3%259D%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25B7%25B1%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E4%25B8%258A-%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%25AB%258A%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%258D%25842%25E5%25B9%25B4&d=vlQcfDRKml8%2F%2BBhsY%2FtEEY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=c88d82ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/175465/%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E8%BF%B7%E7%82%BA%E6%8A%8A%E5%8E%9F%E8%A3%9D%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E7%89%8C-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E4%B8%8A-%E8%AA%8D%E7%88%86%E7%AB%8A%E5%88%A4%E5%85%A5%E7%8D%842%E5%B9%B4</a>"},{"pid":"2f44bb2f78895df5ca1d6b4bdef86e49c4063326","tid":618942,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T08:09:24.000Z","msg":"bus plastic<img src